data.description:
*** Seller offering a $10,000 Buyer Credit ***
This beautiful Rio Del Mar home is a must see! This unique hillside property offers two balconies to enjoy the beautiful views, two decks with a hot tub for your enjoyment and entertainment. The property is all electric and comes with owned solar panels. The home has fresh paint, an updated kitchen, updated bathroom with heated floors and a cobblestone shower. The basement has been conditioned to be a bonus room with a full bathroom. It is currently used a short-term rental. The new owner can choose to integrate it to the rest of the home or continue to use it as a source of income. There are many more upgrades to list. The home is centrally located. SeaCliff State beach, Rio Del Mar Beach and Aptos Village is also a 5 min drive.
